      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个定时抓取法院文档的流程图。核心是用Cloud Scheduler每天触发，然后API层去OSCN抓取，最后存到Database和Cloud Storage两份。",
      "elements_involved": [
