    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。OSCN是俄克拉荷马州法院系统，API从它上面Scrape文档，拿到Documents后分别写入Database做索引，同时归档到Cloud Storage存原始文件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OSCN",
        "API",
        "Documents",
        "Database",
        "Cloud Storage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画出五个participant：Cloud Scheduler、API、Database、OSCN、Cloud Storage。然后画第一条线：Cloud Scheduler调用API的/hydrate端点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cloud Scheduler",
        "API",
        "/hydrate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来API要去OSCN执行Scrape操作，然后OSCN把Documents返回给API。这里OSCN到API用虚线箭头表示响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API",
        "OSCN",
        "Scrape",
        "Documents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：API发起Scrape到OSCN，OSCN返回Documents给API。然后API并行发两份Documents出去，分别到Database和Cloud Storage？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API",
        "OSCN",
        "Documents",
