        "Cloud Storage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，OSCN返回的那条线应该是虚线，我刚才没说清楚。还有API到Database和Cloud Storage的两条线都是实线，表示主动写入，不是返回。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OSCN",
